# Supabase Migrations

1. `supabase migration new <name>` → edit SQL under `supabase/migrations/`.
2. `yarn db:reset` locally and smoke-test affected features.
3. Merge to `main` — GitHub Actions runs `supabase db push` on production.

Local keys from `yarn db:status` into `.env.local`. Preview deploys do not reach local Docker.

Skills: `supabase`, `supabase-postgres-best-practices` under `.cursor/skills/`. Guide: `docs/supabase.md`.
